race.comment: HOSTILE LA VISTA (8) showed his ability two runs back with a determined win at Murwillumbah before being safely held at Eagle Farm last time. He drops back to his winning trip, gets in well with the claim, and the addition of blinkers should sharpen him right up. Expecting a much stronger showing. FUNKY ZEBRA (6) resumed in style at Ipswich, leading throughout for a convincing win. He draws to advantage again and looks capable of building on that effort with further improvement to come. ARIYAH (9) was brave on the Poly last start, scoring narrowly after racing on speed. She should push forward again and give her supporters another bold sight. BILLY BOOM (17) has been consistent in two runs back and looks ready to peak now third-up. STRIKE THE HEART (13) has tactical speed to cross from the wide draw and could pinch it if left alone in front.
